From 36fb302affa1bdc921c4adba1c6f8a67bca8efaa Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vera Aletheia <vera@veraaletheia.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 17:40:13 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] ham pass: real hero image, cleaned stock deps, responsive
 fixes

- Hero: replaced gemini stock laptop with live awdmods.com screenshot
  as the "subject under examination". Callouts now pin ON-screen at the
  image edges with responsive positioning (no more -left-[20%] that
  broke on narrow viewports). Added subtle red redaction-line overlays
  on the screenshot to reinforce the forensic framing.
- Ethics Gate: killed unsplash phone background image, replaced with
  a brass procedural-grid wash (no external dep)
- Methodology: killed unsplash cyber-pipeline background, replaced with
  diagonal orange stripes pattern (no external dep)
- Body + grain: stopped sourcing textures from transparenttextures.com;
  grain is now a pure-CSS SVG data URL fractal-noise filter
- Nav: AUTH_LOGIN -> COMMISSION_AUDIT (buyer commissions, doesn't log in)
- Tiers: Core -> Focus, Spectrum -> Full Spectrum (match source-of-truth)
- Mobile: responsive padding throughout (px-6 sm:px-8, py-20 sm:py-24),
  skew-hero transform disabled under 768px so the image reads flat on
  phones, callouts scale text/max-width for narrow viewports, nav strip
  stacks vertically on mobile
- Vite: allowedHosts: true so cloudflare tunnel can serve the dev server

Copy is still gemini-hallucinated placeholder (per Dan - to be replaced
with real ECP copy later). This pass is strictly structural + assets.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
